{"tid":2140661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美陸軍著手研究下一代主戰車 取代M1 Abrams系列","createTime":"2020-08-05T06:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T07:03:14.000Z","uid":285559,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1f48d6c8fcc52ae616f7ac91373c95b0d26824bf","tid":2140661,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:54:03.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國陸軍開始研究下一代主戰車，目標是取代現役的M1艾布蘭（Abrams）系列，以維持戰場上的絕對優勢。<br />\n<br />\n根據《Defense Blog》報導，美國陸軍車輛研究、開發和工程中心（TARDEC）已啟動「未來決定性殺傷力」（NGCV-FDL）計畫，研究下一代主戰車。為應對未來戰場，美國陸軍希望獲得一種，擁有強大火力，又有超過其他主戰車運動性能的快速戰車。<br />\n<br />\n根據「未來決定性殺傷力」計畫，下一代戰車將具有A-PNT（一種解決失去GPS訊號的定位技術）和彈性網路功能，使未來的戰車編隊能夠執行半獨立行動，同時與空中的直升機、戰機進行聯合行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnZdV7x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnZdV7x.jpg&h=e5c6d88e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iyZJyUc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiyZJyUc.jpg&h=c4024ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從目前美國陸軍作戰能力發展司令部釋出的概念圖來看，下一代戰車將比現有的M1系列、德國豹2戰車更小、更輕。新戰車也將配備現代化的主動防護系統，以防禦反戰車引導飛彈、火箭和高爆彈。<br />\n<br />\n「未來決定性殺傷力」預計在2023年獲得結論，決定美軍下一代主戰車的設計理念。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://defence-blog.com/news/army/u-s-army-develops-next-generation-tank.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdefence-blog.com%2Fnews%2Farmy%2Fu-s-army-develops-next-generation-tank.html&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZearM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=2d3f578e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://defence-blog.com/news/army/u-s-army-develops-next-generation-tank.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3250296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3250296&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZearM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=2318cf40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3250296&h=eafae4f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3250296</a>"},{"pid":"aec92e5be06b90372dbeb04772b49beadc9b935e","tid":2140661,"uid":57,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"根本冇可能取代M1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下一代應該都轉玩無人駕駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}